parts.text:
```json
{
  "application": "BLAST",
  "details": {
    "software": [
      "Blast/ncbi-blast/2.6.0+",
      "UHTS/Analysis/BEDTools/2.26.0",
      "awk",
      "makeblastdb",
      "cut",
      "sort",
      "uniq",
      "comm",
      "mv",
      "rm",
      "find",
      "basename"
    ],
    "resources": {
      "memory": "8GB",
      "cores": 8,
      "queue": "priority",
      "log_files": [
        "../../data/logs/chromoblast.err",
        "../../data/logs/chromoblast.out"
      ]
    },
    "data": {
      "input": [
        "../../data/assoc_mapping/case_control/case_control_hits.tsv",
        "../../data/ref_genome/ordered_genome/merged.fasta"
      ],
      "output": [
        "../../data/homology/blast_files/*.fasta",
        "../../data/homology/blast_files/*.out",
        "../../data/homology/blast_files/*.bed",
        "../../data/homology/blast_files/*.tsv"
      ]
    },
    "description": "This script blasts the chromosomes containing GWAS hits against one-another to identify overlapping alignments and identify genomic regions that may be under similar selective pressures."
  }
}
```
